node.text:
🐿DROP THE PRESSURE🐿

As we draw closer and closer to fall, all the end of the year festivities come to mind: Oktoberfest, our anniversary, Christmas, and of course New Years. So we’re cranking up the volume but never cracking under pressure as we start to drop banger after banger 🕺🏽

Although this little furry mammal may be small in size, he doesn’t disappoint in the flavor he brings. Heaps upon heaps of raspberry and pineapple  swirl through this OG sour, infused with that delightful vanilla and marshmallow goodness we have all come to love 😍

Only one thing left to do..

🐿🍍🐿🍍🐿🍍🐿🍍🐿
🍍DROP THE PRESSURE🍍
🐿🍍🐿🍍🐿🍍🐿🍍🐿
Sour Ale Conditioned it’s Raspberry, Pineapple, Vanilla, and Marshmallow

Loving the pressure with this one

node.text:
💡ITS SHOWTIME💡

Being able to bring back some OG’s, especially one done with homies like @corporateladderbrewing , is always a great feeling for a brewery familia. It signifies you’ve allowed us to go about making outlandish beers long enough to circle back around and drop a re-release, that you’ve stuck by our side and embarked on this trip with us, and we must continue to trust in the process and enjoy the sights along the way.

Bigger, badder, bolder, heavier handed, because why not? But rather because we must. The only thing to do is to stare into the spotlight and give it more than before; This cockatoo has come to do just that. More pineapple, more Peach, more Florida blossom honey.

Back for an encore 🎭

🍑 🍍 🍑 🍍 🍑 🍍 
🍍IT’S SHOWTIME🍑
🍑 🍍 🍑 🍍 🍑 🍍 
Sour Ale Conditioned with Pineapple, Peach, and Florida Blossom Honey

$22/4pk

6%

🆕PRE-ORDER FOR “ IT’S SHOWTIME “ BEGINS SUNDAY, AUGUST 15TH, @ 4:20PM 👀

📦Pick-Up Starts TUESDAY, August 17th @ 4:00PM💨

Back on stage with this one
And as always, 

✌🏽&❤️

#StayTrippy #It’sShowtime #Collab #CorporateLadder

node.text:
🚨SOLD OUT🚨

You heard about the drop, you showed us how much you loved it with all your comments and likes, and you even showed up early and waited in LINE for the taproom to open JUST so you could get your hands on MIAMI’S FIRST SLUSHY XXL and we sold out faster than we could have anticipated🙏🏽

We are absolutely honored to have had the opportunity to brew Miami’s first slushy with our homies from @450northbrewing, and even more honored to have shared it with our community here in SoFlo. We know the cans flew by far too fast, so we’re tapping all that we have left starting tomorrow in our Taproom.

And don’t worry

👀 Keep your eyes out for another SLUSHY 👀

Thank you for always staying trippy with us
❤️❤️ We love you❤️❤️

Catch you all later 
And as always, 

✌🏽& 🍄

#StayTrippy #SOLDOUT #450NorthBrewing #MiamiSlushyXXL

node.text:
🍻GUAVA TOAST & RUBBER DUCKIES 🍻

One of the finest things in life is all that which you reserve for family; Those Sunday potlucks, chicken fights in the pool, talks of life and love, sipping lagers deep into the night 🌙

Uncle @dinosvino and everyone @vitaminseabrewing radiate what family is all about, always exuding all the love and respect they have to possibly give. We both wanted to toast to family, so we brewed up a lager as crispy as toast and conditioned it with a splash of guava. 

Sipping on Sundays is recommended. Don’t forget your rubber duckies🛁

🐤 🐤 🐤 🐤 🐤 🐤 🐤 🐤 🐤 🐤 🐤 
🐤GUAVA TOAST & RUBBER DUCKIES🐤

node.text:
💀BARRELS OF DEATH💀 

Here is to keeping things in their purest form. To Leaving them unadulterated and untouched by anything other than their essential and elemental characteristics. To insisting, with reckless abandon, certain things are just meant to be left alone; Unbothered, unchanged, unconditioned.

That’s exactly what we did with this stout: left it in its purest form. Aged 21 months in both Dominican Rum barrels and Woodford Reserve Bourbon barrels, we let the base and the barrels do the talking.

Silken Elegance in ever bottle.

☠️☠️☠️☠️☠️☠️☠️☠️☠️
☠️BARRELS OF DEATH☠️

node.text:
🚀DUDE, WHERE’S MY ROCKET?👨🏽‍🚀

Ever start a company and use it’s profits to build yourself a rocket ? Yeah, neither have we 😅 but we can appreciate a hearty desire for experimentation and exploration, because hey.. we have to keep things eccentric and trippy 🍄 🍄 🍄

Sometimes you just have to shake things up, so in keeping with that sentiment we procured some EXPERIMENTAL hops and dosed a stellar DIPA so hazy it’ll have you singing with the birds up in space

Their Origin might not be Blue, but they’ll still have you floating with the stars 😉🤩

🦤🚀 🦤🚀 🦤🚀 🦤🚀 🦤🚀🦤
🚀DUDE, WHERE’S MY ROCKET?🚀
🦤🚀 🦤🚀 🦤🚀 🦤🚀 🦤🚀🦤

node.text:
⚓️LOAD OF BARNACLES⚓️

It’s that time of year again where we make our way down to the sea floor with our homies from @calusabrewing to find out who lives in a pineapple, maybe stop by trippyfish fields and pick some aquatic hops , and then make our way home just in time for supper and our first hop addition 😉

We transmute our experience into a liquid bountiful deep sea mosaic and galaxy, washed ashore by motueka, that elicits a full submersion of your taste buds. Although we traveled through crystalline waters to get these hops, HAZY is the only word to describe their gifts.

Take a sip, you might just get hit by a..

🦑🐠🐳🐚⚓️ 🦑🐠🐳🐚
⚓️LOAD OF BARNACLES ⚓️ 
🦑🐠🐳🐚⚓️ 🦑🐠🐳🐚

Triple India Pale Ale Hopped with Galaxy, Mosaic, and Motueka Hops

$22/4PK

10% ABV
